OL,3,CResearch proposes justice system
OL,4,Coverhaul for victims of institutional
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FA new justice framework is required to
OL,8,Fbetter meet the needs of victims and
OL,9,Fsurvivors of non-recent institutional
OL,10,Fabuse across the island of Ireland, a
OL,11,Fresearch project has suggested.
OL,13,FThe academics behind the new research
OL,14,Fsaid they had highlighted
OL,15,F"shortcomings in current legal and
OL,16,Fjustice processes" such as inquiries
OL,17,Fand redress schemes.
