OL,3,CResearch proposes justice system
OL,4,Coverhaul for victims of institutional
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe research was undertaken by
OL,8,FProfessor Anne-Marie McAlinden from
OL,9,FQueen's University Belfast, Professor
OL,10,FMarie Keenan from University College
OL,11,FDublin (UCD), and Dr James Gallen from
OL,12,FDublin City University (DCU).
OL,14,FThe issue of historical institutional
OL,15,Fabuses in multiple settings has led to
OL,16,Fseveral investigations and redress
OL,17,Fschemes in Northern Ireland and the
OL,18,FRepublic of Ireland over a number of
OL,19,Fyears.
