OL,3,CResearch proposes justice system
OL,4,Coverhaul for victims of institutional
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,FThe research project involved
OL,8,Finterviews with 74 stakeholders,
OL,9,Fincluding survivors, legal
OL,10,Fprofessionals, and institutional
OL,11,F(church and state) representatives.
OL,13,FIt also drew on international
OL,14,Fexperiences of justice responses to
OL,15,Fnon-recent institutional abuses such
OL,16,Fas inquiries, redress schemes and
OL,17,Fapologies.
