OL,7,FIt said that central to this new
OL,8,Fapproach is "increasing engagement
OL,9,Fbetween victim/survivors and
OL,10,Finstitutional actors".
OL,12,FThe research calls for reforms to
OL,13,Flegal culture; truth-seeking processes
OL,14,Fand redress.
OL,16,FKey findings and recommendations
OL,17,Finclude:
