OL,7,FProfessor Marie Keenan from the School
OL,8,Fof Social Policy, Social Work and
OL,9,FSocial Justice at UCD said: "From the
OL,10,Foutset we were determined to include
OL,11,Fall voices and listen carefully to the
OL,12,Flived experience of victim/survivors
OL,13,Fand responsible institutional actors
OL,14,Fin church and state; examine the
OL,15,Ftemporal challenges involved in non-
OL,16,Frecent institutional abuses and how
OL,17,Fthese contribute to the responsibility/
OL,18,Faccountability gap, and, analyse the
OL,19,Fpotential for innovative justice
OL,20,Fthinking influenced by restorative and
OL,21,Ftransitional justice philosophies.
