OL,7,F"We found there is an appetite for a
OL,8,Fnew way and offer suggestions as to
OL,9,Fhow this can be done."
OL,11,FDr James Gallen from the School of Law
OL,12,Fand Government at DCU said:
OL,13,F"Addressing non-recent institutional
OL,14,Fabuses remains a pressing and ongoing
OL,15,Fchallenge for societies globally.
OL,17,F"Several justice responses remain
OL,18,Fongoing or in negotiations or
OL,19,Fproposals on the island of Ireland."
